ria]] HD\n*[[Ici ARTV]] HD\n*[[Ici Explora]] HD\n*[[Ici RDI]] HD\n*[[Investigation (TV channel)|Investigation]] HD\n*[[Le Canal Nouvelles|LCN]] HD\n*[[MOI&cie (TV channel)|MOI&cie]] HD\n*[[MusiMax]] HD\n*[[MusiquePlus]] HD\n*[[Plan\u00e8te+|Plan\u00e8te+ Canada]] HD\n*[[Prise 2]] HD\n*[[R\u00e9seau des sports|RDS]] HD\n*[[RDS2]] HD\n*[[RDS Info]] HD\n*[[S\u00e9ries+]] HD\n*[[T\u00e9l\u00e9magino]] HD\n*[[T\u00e9l\u00e9toon]] HD\n*[[TVA Sports]] HD\n*[[TVA Sports|TVA Sports 2]] HD\n*[[TV5 Qu\u00e9bec Canada|TV5]] HD\n*[[Unis (TV channel)|Unis]] HD\n*[[Vrak]] HD\n*[[Yoopa]] HD\n*[[Zeste]] HD\n*[[Z (TV channel)|Z]] HD\n{{div col end}}\n\n===French PayTV===\n*[[Cin\u00e9pop]] HD\n*[[Super \u00c9cran]] HD\n*[[Super \u00c9cran]] 2 HD\n*[[Super \u00c9cran]] 3 HD\n*[[Super \u00c9cran]] 4 HD\n\n===French PPV===\n*[[Canal Indigo]] HD\n*[[Vu!]] HD\n\n==English HD Channels==\n\n===Canadian English Conventional===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Network !! Channel\n|-\n|rowspan=\"13\"| [[CBC Television|CBC]] || [[CBLT-DT]] Toronto\n|-\n| [[CBMT-DT]] Montreal\n|-\n| [[CBUT-DT]] Vancouver\n|-\n| [[CBOT-DT]] Ottawa\n|-\n| [[CBXT-DT]] Edmonton\n|-\n| [[CBRT-DT]] Calgary\n|-\n| [[CBWT-DT]] Winnipeg\n|-\n| [[CBHT-DT]] Halifax\n|-\n| [[CBAT-DT]] Fredericton\n|-\n| [[CBET-DT]] Windsor\n|-\n| [[CBNT-DT]] St. John's\n|-\n| [[CBKT-DT]] Regina\n|-\n| [[CBCT-DT]] Charlottetown\n|-\n|rowspan=\"15\"| [[CTV Television Network|CTV]] || [[CFTO-DT]] Toronto\n|-\n| [[CFCF-DT]] Montreal\n|-\n| [[CIVT-DT]] Vancouver\n|-\n| [[CJOH-DT]] Ottawa\n|-\n| [[CFRN-DT]] Edmonton\n|-\n| [[CFCN-DT]] Calgary\n|-\n| [[CKY-DT]] Winnipeg\n|-\n| [[CKCO-DT]] Kitchener\n|-\n| [[CJCH-DT]] Halifax\n|-\n| [[CKLT-DT]] Saint John (OTA only)\n|-\n| [[CKCW-DT]] Moncton\n|-\n| [[CFQC-DT]] Saskatoon\n|-\n| [[CKCK-DT]] Regina\n|-\n| [[CKPR-DT]] Thunder Bay\n|-\n| [[CITL-DT]] Lloydminster (OTA only)\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\"| [[CTV Two]] || [[CKVR-DT]] Barrie\n|-\n| [[CIVI-DT]] Victoria\n|-\n| [[CHRO-DT]] Pembroke\n|-\n| [[CFPL-DT]] Lon